| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6019 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 568e78dc-8b18-5884-a0a5-c9e2d4116e79"
